This repository contains information related to the tool Verily presented at ICSE-2014 by John L. Singleton, Gary T. Leavens. The tool was originally presented in this <a href="http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?doid=2591062.2591069">paper.</a>

This repository is not the original repository for this tool. Here are some links to the original project:

The Official Project <a href="http://goverily.org">Page</a>, including binaries for tool
Source Code forked from Original repository of tool

In this repository, for Verily you will find:
:white_check_mark: Source code (available)
:white_check_mark: The original tool (available)
